{"tid":1516074,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"身為黃絲既你，我唔明點解你呢一刻都唔起身邊d藍絲，同狗底？ 我真係好撚忟","createTime":"2019-08-29T12:08:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T12:39:41.000Z","uid":278698,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4d4344e15af435fd3ea50deabb76fe2e3eb996d8","tid":1516074,"uid":278698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:08:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">可能你地覺得佢地仲係你朋友</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">可能你覺得佢同你有好好既回憶</span></span><br />\n<br />\n可能你驚圈子太細，會比人反起底。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但我請你好好記住，衣家係白色恐怖既時候<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你本身已經唔會上前線，又唔會比人拉，又唔會比人除杉，又唔洗爆眼，依家叫你做少少野去backup受壓迫既一群都唔肯？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你對唔對d義士啊？ 我地就係要藍色被起底，或被整既數量愈多，咁先可以保障到受白色恐怖既員工安全啊<br />\n<br />\n唔好再同我婦仁之仁，自己做野<br />\n<br />\n以上係玩食雞果陣既情況，不是現實。"},{"pid":"1594214026466ae9361aee6a9cb5ddcbac2d0be9","tid":1516074,"uid":278698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:27:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"68dd1420130a47241d6ddcaf104c74922c061181","tid":1516074,"uid":92836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:39:41.000Z","msg":"毋忘聽日830香港重光紀念日。<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><em>830中環見<br />\n830中環見<br />\n830中環見</em></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/96PXdYs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F96PXdYs.jpg&h=2d869ee7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4KF8LYC.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4KF8LYC.gif&h=64c0bd73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n［行動Post］ 830 感謝勇武暨重光紀念日行動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1511085\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1511085</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}